{
  "stem": "15082.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got there, some of my cousins were there-- somebody of the Olaska family, and the Stein family, and the Horowitz family, and my father's two brothers with their family.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the forest towards a Polish village which was a little more friendlier than the Ukrainian type of villages.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were able to go in the evening and get some food from them, whether you bought it or they gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd cook in the forest, make a little fire, try to keep the fire very low, because of the Germans cannot see the smoke coming out, because otherwise you'd give away where you are.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what I recall is the high holidays spending there, and all of us standing wrapped up and praying, saying [NON-ENGLISH] in the darkness of the night.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Rabbi was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Yitzak Homilen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And we went through [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After that, my father says that there's no way we're going to be able to survive here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At night, a few times we were assailed by Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't kill us then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just robbed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whatever little possessions you still had, you held on to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at one point on a Friday night, my dad says, we better get out of here, and go back to see if we can talk to Mr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Marczeniek that he would take us in permanently.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We started walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In order to go to-- and this was-- the village name was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to go to [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to cross a road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was coming out of this forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
